<qti-assessment-item xmlns="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0" xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" identifier="Q64_v2" title="Q64_v2" time-dependent="false" adaptive="false" xsi:schemaLocation="http://www.imsglobal.org/xsd/imsqtiasi_v3p0 https://purl.imsglobal.org/spec/qti/v3p0/schema/xsd/imsqti_asiv3p0_v1p0.xsd">
  <qti-response-declaration identifier="RESPONSE" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier">
    <qti-correct-response>
      <qti-value>ChoiceB</qti-value>
    </qti-correct-response>
  </qti-response-declaration>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="FEEDBACK" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SOLUTION" cardinality="single" base-type="identifier"/>
  <qti-outcome-declaration identifier="SCORE" cardinality="single" base-type="float">
    <qti-default-value>
      <qti-value>0</qti-value>
    </qti-default-value>
  </qti-outcome-declaration>
  <qti-item-body>
    <p>
      En una caja hay 30 fichas rojas, azules y verdes, todas indistinguibles al tacto. Al sacar una ficha al azar, se tiene la siguiente información sobre la probabilidad del evento:<br />
      <br />
      Evento | Probabilidad<br />
      "roja o azul" | 
      <m:math>
        <m:mfrac>
          <m:mn>4</m:mn>
          <m:mn>5</m:mn>
        </m:mfrac>
      </m:math>
    </p>
    <p>
      Según esta información, ¿cuántas fichas verdes hay en la caja?
    </p>
    <qti-choice-interaction response-identifier="RESPONSE" max-choices="1" shuffle="false">
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceA">24<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceA" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si hubiera 24 fichas verdes, entonces las fichas que son rojas o azules serían <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. En ese caso, la probabilidad de sacar una ficha roja o azul sería <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, que se simplifica a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>1</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, y no a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceB">6<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceB" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">¡Correcto! Si la probabilidad de sacar una ficha roja o azul es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, entonces la cantidad de fichas rojas o azules es <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. Por lo tanto, las fichas verdes son <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceC">26<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceC" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si hubiera 26 fichas verdes, entonces las fichas que son rojas o azules serían <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>26</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. En ese caso, la probabilidad de sacar una ficha roja o azul sería <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, que se simplifica a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>2</m:mn><m:mn>15</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, y no a <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
      
      <qti-simple-choice identifier="ChoiceD">30<qti-feedback-inline identifier="FB_ChoiceD" outcome-identifier="FEEDBACK">Incorrecto. Si hubiera 30 fichas verdes, entonces no habría fichas rojas ni azules, porque <m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>. En ese caso, la probabilidad de sacar una ficha roja o azul sería <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>0</m:mn><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>, es decir, <m:math><m:mn>0</m:mn></m:math>, y no <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>.</qti-feedback-inline></qti-simple-choice>
    </qti-choice-interaction>
    <qti-feedback-block identifier="show" outcome-identifier="SOLUTION" show-hide="show">
      <qti-content-body>
        <p><strong>Resolución paso a paso</strong></p>
        <ol>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 1: Interpretar la probabilidad dada</strong></p>
            <p>La probabilidad de sacar una ficha roja o azul es <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math>. Como en total hay 30 fichas, eso significa que <m:math><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac></m:math> del total corresponde a fichas rojas o azules.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 2: Calcular cuántas fichas son rojas o azules</strong></p>
            <p>Calculamos <m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math>.</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mfrac><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mn>5</m:mn></m:mfrac><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>4</m:mn><m:mo>×</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
            <p>Entonces, hay 24 fichas que son rojas o azules.</p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Paso 3: Calcular cuántas fichas verdes hay</strong></p>
            <p>Como el total de fichas es 30, las fichas verdes son las que faltan:</p>
            <p><m:math><m:mrow><m:mn>30</m:mn><m:mo>−</m:mo><m:mn>24</m:mn><m:mo>=</m:mo><m:mn>6</m:mn></m:mrow></m:math></p>
          </li>
          <li>
            <p><strong>Conclusión</strong></p>
            <p>En la caja hay 6 fichas verdes. La alternativa correcta es la B.</p>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </qti-content-body>
    </qti-feedback-block>
  </qti-item-body>
  <qti-response-processing>
    <qti-response-condition>
      <qti-response-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SCORE">
          <qti-base-value base-type="float">1</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceB</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceC</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else-if>
        <qti-match>
          <qti-variable identifier="RESPONSE"/>
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-match>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceD</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else-if>
      <qti-response-else>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="FEEDBACK">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">FB_ChoiceA</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
        <qti-set-outcome-value identifier="SOLUTION">
          <qti-base-value base-type="identifier">show</qti-base-value>
        </qti-set-outcome-value>
      </qti-response-else>
    </qti-response-condition>
  </qti-response-processing>
</qti-assessment-item>